modules.description: Handles SMTP protocol operations such as connecting, sending EHLO, MAIL, RCPT, DATA, and QUIT commands. Works with socket connections, email headers, and message bodies to facilitate email transmission. Used to build custom SMTP clients or servers with TLS support and asynchronous capabilities.

Provides functions to submit and send email messages over SMTP, supporting TLS and authentication. Operates with network connections, email paths, and message encoding/decoding structures. Used for sending emails through a specified server with customizable transport and security settings.
